HEADWORD: Hogreeve
<hw>Hog"reeve`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Reeve</er>.]</ety> <def>A civil officer charged with the duty of
impounding hogs running at large.</def> <mark>[New Eng.]</mark>
<rj><au>Bartlett.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
